data.description:
Welcome to this stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home located inside a gated community. Upon entry you will notice the beautiful hardwood floors that flow throughout the living area. The kitchen has been updated and has ample counter space. The dining room is the perfect spot for entertaining and the office has plenty of space and tons of natural light. The living room has a gorgeous fireplace, perfect for the chilly evenings. 
Upstairs is as sprawling master suite complete with a bonus room that would make the perfect nursery or private lounge area. The master bath is huge and has a double vanity, soaking tub, separate shower and walk in closet. Additionally, there are three generously sized guest bedrooms and a full bathroom, ensuring plenty space for family or guests. The outdoor space is equally impressive and features a massive back porch and adorable play house. Brand new roof!
All of this is located in Jones County just minutes to I-75 and North Macon.
